<P1group>
<Title>Validity of things done and continuity of charges incurred</Title>
<P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/836/article/3/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/836/article/3" id="article-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/836/article/3/1/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/836/article/3/1" id="article-3-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>This Order does not affect the validity of anything done by or in relation to a police area returning officer designated by the 2024 Order before the coming into force of this Order.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/836/article/3/2/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/836/article/3/2" id="article-3-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Any charges incurred for specified services or specified expenses by a police area returning officer designated for a police area by the 2024 Order before the coming into force of this Order are to be treated as having been incurred by the police area returning officer who is designated for the same police area following the coming into force of this Order for the purpose of each maximum recoverable amount for that police area.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2024/836/article/3/3/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2024/836/article/3/3" id="article-3-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>In this article—</Text>
<UnorderedList Class="Definition" Decoration="none">
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>“<Term id="term-maximum-recoverable-amount">maximum recoverable amount</Term>” means the amount specified in, as the case may be, column (2), (3) or (4) of the table in Schedule 3 to the Police and Crime Commissioner Elections (Local Returning Officers’ and Police Area Returning Officers’ Charges) Order 2024<FootnoteRef Ref="f00005"/>;</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>
<Text>“<Term id="term-specified-services">specified services</Term>” and “<Term id="term-specified-expenses">specified expenses</Term>” have the same meaning as in Article 3 of the Police and Crime Commissioner Elections (Local Returning Officers’ and Police Area Returning Officers’ Charges) Order 2024.</Text>
</Para>
</ListItem>
</UnorderedList>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
